data.description: Check out this unique home with 3 bedrooms / 2.5 baths on 5.65 acres per public record!!! It has a separate dining-room, step down family-room, bonus room that is used for an office, laundry area, and a big room with a sink in it and it will be going with the seller. Kitchen has granite counter tops with a lot of cabinets & counter space. There is a big screened in area in the back for you to enjoy the fresh air while cooking out on your grill. There is a 40 x 60 shop - barn to store items in or make it into a game-room. All of the property is fenced in with two gates in the front. Seller is a dog groomer, she needs at least a six hour notice, so she can have the dogs put up. They need a week to get their stuff moved out after the closing.
